snippet.title: Dick Tracy gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Dick Tracy, Dos PC game produced by Titus Interactive in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/dick-tracy/5909/
Playing through the first stage of this difficult arcade game featuring Dick Tracy detective.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
